query:
INSERT INTO guestReviews (source, externalId, reviewerName, reviewerCountry, rating, title, content, language, sentiment, topics, apartmentCode, hasReply, replyContent, replyDate, reviewDate) VALUES
('google', 'g_001', 'Alexander Petrov', 'Russia', 5, 'Perfect sea view apartment!', 'Amazing location with stunning Black Sea views. The apartment was spotlessly clean and modern. Staff was incredibly helpful with check-in. Will definitely return!', 'en', 'positive', '["location", "cleanliness", "service", "view"]', 'A-1205', true, 'Thank you so much for your wonderful review! We are delighted you enjoyed the sea views and our service. Looking forward to welcoming you back!', '2025-12-10 14:30:00', '2025-12-08 10:15:00'),
('google', 'g_002', 'Maria Kowalska', 'Poland', 5, 'Best vacation ever', 'Exceeded all expectations! The apartment was luxurious, clean, and had everything we needed. The location is perfect - close to beach and restaurants.', 'en', 'positive', '["cleanliness", "amenities", "location"]', 'B-0803', true, 'Dear Maria, thank you for choosing ORBI City! We are thrilled to hear about your wonderful experience. Hope to see you again soon!', '2025-12-05 11:20:00', '2025-12-03 16:45:00'),
('google', 'g_003', 'John Smith', 'USA', 4, 'Great stay, minor issues', 'Beautiful apartment with amazing views. Only issue was the WiFi was a bit slow for video calls. Otherwise perfect!', 'en', 'positive', '["view", "wifi"]', 'A-1508', true, 'Thank you John! We appreciate your feedback about the WiFi - we have upgraded our internet infrastructure. Hope to host you again!', '2025-12-02 09:00:00', '2025-11-28 20:30:00'),
('google', 'g_004', 'Elena Ivanova', 'Ukraine', 5, 'Чудовий відпочинок!', 'Прекрасні апартаменти з видом на море. Все було ідеально - чистота, сервіс, розташування. Дякуємо!', 'uk', 'positive', '["cleanliness", "service", "location", "view"]', 'C-0612', false, NULL, NULL, '2025-12-15 08:20:00'),
('google', 'g_005', 'Ahmed Hassan', 'UAE', 5, 'Luxury experience', 'Five star service in a beautiful location. The apartment was modern and well-equipped. Highly recommend for families!', 'en', 'positive', '["service", "amenities", "family-friendly"]', 'A-2001', true, 'Thank you Ahmed! We are honored by your kind words. ORBI City is always ready to welcome you and your family!', '2025-12-12 15:45:00', '2025-12-10 11:00:00'),
('google', 'g_006', 'Sophie Martin', 'France', 3, 'Good but noisy', 'Nice apartment and great location, but there was construction noise during the day. Staff tried to help by offering earplugs.', 'en', 'neutral', '["noise", "location", "service"]', 'B-0405', true, 'Dear Sophie, we sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. The construction has now been completed. We hope you will give us another chance!', '2025-11-25 10:30:00', '2025-11-20 14:15:00'),
('google', 'g_007', 'Dmitry Volkov', 'Russia', 5, 'Отличный отдых в Батуми', 'Шикарные апартаменты с потрясающим видом на море. Чисто, уютно, современно. Персонал очень отзывчивый. Рекомендую!', 'ru', 'positive', '["view", "cleanliness", "service"]', 'A-1712', false, NULL, NULL, '2025-12-14 09:30:00'),
('google', 'g_008', 'Lisa Anderson', 'UK', 5, 'Wonderful holiday', 'Everything was perfect from start to finish. The apartment was exactly as pictured, clean and comfortable. Great communication from the team.', 'en', 'positive', '["accuracy", "cleanliness", "communication"]', 'C-0915', true, 'Thank you Lisa! We pride ourselves on accurate listings and great communication. See you next time!', '2025-12-08 16:00:00', '2025-12-05 12:30:00'),
('google', 'g_009', 'Giorgi Beridze', 'Georgia', 4, 'კარგი გამოცდილება', 'ძალიან კარგი ბინა და მდებარეობა. ოდნავ ძვირია, მაგრამ ხარისხი შეესაბამება ფასს.', 'ka', 'positive', '["location", "value", "quality"]', 'B-1103', false, NULL, NULL, '2025-12-13 17:45:00'),
('google', 'g_010', 'Anna Müller', 'Germany', 5, 'Perfekter Urlaub', 'Wunderschöne Wohnung mit Meerblick. Alles war sauber und modern. Das Personal war sehr freundlich und hilfsbereit.', 'de', 'positive', '["view", "cleanliness", "service"]', 'A-0908', true, 'Vielen Dank Anna! Wir freuen uns sehr über Ihre positive Bewertung. Bis zum nächsten Mal!', '2025-12-11 13:20:00', '2025-12-09 10:00:00');
